<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About WanderWise</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="./img/chatbot.png">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f242d, #34495e);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #ecf0f1;
    }

    .navbar {
      background-color: #0ef;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar a {
      color: #1f242d;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      background: #2c3e50;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    h1, h3 {
      color: #0ef;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #0ef;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      list-style: square;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #95a5a6;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">
      <a href="/">WanderWise AI</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>About <span class="highlight">WanderWise</span></h1>

    <p><strong>WanderWise</strong> is your smart adventure planner, powered by Gemini AI. Whether you're into hiking, surfing, snowboarding, or exploring hidden gems, WanderWise delivers personalized, real-time travel ideas and safety insights—just for you.</p>

    <p>Our AI understands your interests naturally and offers curated suggestions—from scenic routes to off-the-grid spots, building <span class="highlight">experiences that stay with you</span>.</p>

    <h3>Core Features:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Tailored trip suggestions</li>
      <li>Real destinations with rich data</li>
      <li>Adventure activity recommendations</li>
      <li>Conversational AI for instant ideas</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="footer">
      Crafted with passion by <strong>Anup Pandey</strong><br>
      Powered by Gemini API
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>